resource.title: Treatment plan for liver cirrhosis
resource.description: Comprehensive treatment plan including Liver transplant surgery, Post-operative care, Rehabilitation

resource.conclusion: Patient shows improving status for liver cirrhosis. Aisha Nguyen, a 55-year-old Asian female with severe liver cirrhosis underwent a successful liver transplant surgery on June 15, 2020. She is currently in the post-transplant rehabilitation phase and showing steady improvement in liver function.
